H0.text: Which English town's Anglo Saxon name was Gipeswic pronounced Gipperswick. Norwich

H1.text: Which English town's Anglo Saxon name was Gipeswic pronounced Gipperswick. Bury St Edmunds

H2.text: Which English town's Anglo Saxon name was Gipeswic pronounced Gipperswick. Colchester

H3.text: Which English town's Anglo Saxon name was Gipeswic pronounced Gipperswick. Ipswich

A4.text: Ipswich was first recorded during the medieval period as Gippeswic, the town has also been recorded as Gyppewicus and Yppswyche.
